      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-piv-velocity-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV vs CFD velocity field comparison at 3 operating points",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements at 2500, 3500, and 4500 RPM compared against RANS CFD predictions. Mean absolute error in normalized velocity magnitude was 4.2% across all planes. Supports confidence in flow field fidelity for hemolysis index computation."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-hemolysis-index-bench",
