      "name": "Bench hemolysis index validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "Relative hemolysis index predicted by the power-law hemolysis model was compared to in vitro measurements from the FDA generic pump benchmark dataset. Model predictions fell within ±15% of measured RH values across all 5 flow-speed combinations, satisfying the MRL 2 validation requirement."
    }
